{"tid":1290535,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"研究生會明開週年會員大會 提出多項修改 擬刪須用繁體字條文","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:47:30.000Z","uid":268777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1dcf8d852be59870e9f84b292533520b8e320844","tid":1290535,"uid":268777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"有人報夢話HKU研究生會班大陸學生搞事，<br />\n麻煩大家幫推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.undergrad.hk/17546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undergrad.hk%2F17546&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zeCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=1a237606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.undergrad.hk/17546</a><br />\n<br />\n【學苑專訊】香港大學研究生會（PGSA）將於明日（7月7日）下午兩時於香港大學王賡武講堂舉行週年會員大會（Annual General Meeting）討論修改憲章條文事議，包括：<br />\n<br />\n一．刪除指明須用繁體中文以書寫中文的規定；<br />\n<br />\n二．強調研究生會作為香港警察註冊社團，所有有關研究生會的活動需要符合基本法；<br />\n<br />\n三．把修改憲法的門檻要求降低，包括修改憲章的法定會議從週年會員大會（Annual General Meeting）改成普通會員大會（General Meeting），另把修憲的七日通知期改為五日。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本次召開修改憲章的週年會員大會電郵通知發出日期為7月1日，而開會日期為7月7日，通知期不足七日，懷疑違反憲章條例。同時，週年會員大會亦沒有設有最低法定人數。據讀者提供的資訊，在最近一次的全民投票時，投票站並沒設立獨立投票空間，更有投票站的人員站立於投票者前觀察投票者的投票選擇；在該次投票中亦無表明有第三方監察和點票。<br />\n<br />\n早前，研究生會於6月13日發表了一份公告，指「示威者暴力衝突警隊」使警察使用武器，並譴責示威者使用暴力和一切煽動使用暴力的言論。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學研究生會為校內研究生組織，主要為研究生服務，在憲章下設有全民大會、幹事會、評議會及全民投票的制度，架構類近香港大學學生會。現任研究生會主席Li Jingxian正修讀哲學系碩士課程。"},{"pid":"5d48bfe7eaf575a5507edc7096aa208e3cfa2f43","tid":1290535,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"773bec54f851cb61019a5f6c5a13f3f54c113508","tid":1290535,"uid":138314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"唔係HKU<br />\n不過幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9bad321aa952600d3d2c38d5553617c49a9d32","tid":1290535,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be383e5a9930eb8ab4236847f2ec1299b23ca50a","tid":1290535,"uid":33668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港大學 有香港兩隻字都係大陸人 屌"},{"pid":"f92f7d7bfd8ddc36d49d6c9e51c656e3557f2009","tid":1290535,"uid":268777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"香港01報道：<br />\n<strong>港大研究生會周日審議修訂會章 刪「須用繁體中文」及降修憲門檻<br />\n</strong><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/349004/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E7%AB%A0-%E5%88%AA-%E9%A0%88%E7%94%A8%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-%E5%8F%8A%E9%99%8D%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR2RiQ_D-FIxLhvmGvryjjmsC7zhABhzKeIAzb9NS5nua3V_ccyfEYyap9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F349004%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E5%2588%25AA-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%25B9%2581%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2586%25B2%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%26fbclid%3DIwAR2RiQ_D-FIxLhvmGvryjjmsC7zhABhzKeIAzb9NS5nua3V_ccyfEYyap9Y&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zeCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=d9540c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%